channel.name: 👑・daily-leaderboard
channel.topic: Each day, the top 30 players from the daily leaderboard will be showcased on this channel.

messages.content:
Tips on getting a high score:
- Finish as many fights as possible using fewest turns.
- Successful critical hits and kills boost your score, while failed rolls will reduce it, unless a failed roll is reversed.
- Try to use dice and trinkets efficiently, unless it leads to a kill or critical.
- Taking damage lowers your score, unless healed back.
